<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3744430">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3744430/" class="title-link">鲍威尔：奥巴马是穆斯林又怎么样？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3744430"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/shaqingqing/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1385730-68.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/shaqingqing/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">BBpanda</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-09-27"
      class="main-meta">2010-09-27 15:55:56</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3744430_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  在布什政府前前后后众多阁员中，威望最高者当属前任国务卿科林－鲍威尔（Colin Luther Powell）。无论是作为军人还是政治家，鲍威尔都是美国多年来少见的实干型人才。  　　  身为黑人而又不杨于型，但鲍威尔却成为奥巴马之前非洲裔美国人中的“第一高官”，开创诸多先河：第一...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3744430/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">14有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
